title: YouTube Kids
recentChanges: By popular request, we're giving parents more power than ever before. You now have even more control and can hand-pick every channel and video that your child sees.

title: Netflix
recentChanges:
Want to watch Netflix on your phone while dad watches on the TV and grandma watches on her tablet? Live the dream. Just make sure you have the latest update.

And in this release, we fixed bugs and made performance improvements. Just for you.

title: Hulu: Stream TV, Movies & more
recentChanges:
What did the bugs say before we squashed them? May Day! (Hey, we’re TV lovers, not comedians).

Besides a routine pest control, this release includes accessibility improvements and performance enhancements to continue offering the best streaming experience. Enjoy your Hulu favorites!
